quran[24]{c,v,t}:
  26,10,"Oo waa tii Rabbigaa uu u dhawaaqay Muuse (Isagoo leh): U tag dadkaa gar ma qaatayaasha ah"
  26,11,"Qoladaa Fircoon, miyaanay iska jireyn (xumaha oo u hoggaansameyn Allaah)"
  26,12,"wuxuu yidhi: Rabbiyow! Hubaal waxaan ka cabsi qabaa inay i beeniyaan"
  26,13,"Oo ay cidhiidhi noqoto laabteydu, oo cod kari waayo carrabkaygu. Ee u dir Haaruun (inuu i caawiyo)"
  26,14,"Oo waxay igu heystaan danbi (dil aan geystey ah), sidaas darteed waxaan ka cabsi qabaa inay i dilaan"
  26,15,"(Alle) wuxuu yidhi: “Ma jirto! Ee la taga idinku Aayadahayaga. Hubaal; Annagaa idinla jirna oo idin maqleyna"
  26,16,"Ee u taga Fircoon oo ku dhaha: “Hubaal innagu waxaanu nahay Rusuulka Rabbiga uunanka"
  26,17,Ee nagu dar hana raacaane ilmihii Israa’iil
  26,18,"(Fircoon) wuxuu yidhi: Ma waanaan kugu barbaarin dhexdayada adigoo ilmo yar ah? O aad nala joogin sannado badan ka mid ah noloshaada"
  26,19,Oo waxaad fashay falkaagii aad fashay (dishay nin). Oo waxaad adigu ka mid tahay abaal laawayaasha
  26,20,"Wuxuu yidhi: “Waan falay haddaba anigoo ka mid ah kuwaa aan wax garanayn"
  26,21,"Markaas baan idinka cararay markaan idinka cabsaday, markaasuu Rabbigay I siiyey xikmad, oo iga dhigay mid ka mid ah Rususha"
  26,22,"Oo taasi ma nicmad baa aad iigu lib-sheegato, adigoo addoonsaday ilmihii Israa’iil"
  26,23,"Fircoon wuxuu yidhi: Oo muxuu yahay Rabbiga uunanka"
  26,24,"Wuxuu yidhi: “Waa Rabbiga samooyinka iyo arlada iyo waxa u dhexeeya, haddii aad rumeysaneysaan"
  26,25,"Fircoon wuxuu ku yidhi kuwii hareera joogay: Ma waydaan maqleyn"
  26,26,"(Muuse) Wuxuu yidhi:(Allaah) Rabbigiin iyo Rabbiga aabbayaashiinnii hore"
  26,27,"(Fircoon) wuxuu yidhi3: Hubaal Rasulkiinna la idiin soo diray xaqiiq waa waalan yahay"
  26,28,"(Muuse) wuxuu yidhi: Waa Rabbiga bariga iyo galbeedka iyo inta u dhexeysa, haddii aad caqli leedihiin"
  26,29,"(Fircoon) wuxuu yidhi: Haddii aad yeelato ilaah kale aan aniga ahayn, Waxaan kaa mid dhigayaa kuwa xiran"
  26,30,"(Muuse) wuxuu yidhi: “Ma xitaa haddii aan kuula imaado wax (xujo) cad"
  26,31,"Fircoon wuxuu yidhi: Haddaba la imow, haddii aad ka mid tahay run sheegyada"
  26,32,"Markaas buu (Muuse) tuuray ushiisii, mise waa mas muuqda"
  26,33,"Oo wuxuu soo saaray gacantiisii mise, waa mid u cad kuwa eegaya"